Protesting truck drivers have traffic in and around Tshwane backed up, our sister paper Pretoria East Rekord reported.Motorists have been advised to avoid the R21; the N4 between R512 and Mooinooi; the N12; the N14 near Jean Avenue; the N1 North near Garsfontein Road; and the N1 North after the Rigel exit.To read the full story and see video click here: Pretoria East Rekord Read more news by the Middelburg Observer and check out our Facebook, follow us on Twitter or Instagram